OL,4,G1800FQueen: Classic Albums
OL,5,     GA Night At The Opera: It featured
OL,6,     Ghits Bohemian Rhapsody and You're
OL,7,     GMy Best Friend and propelled the
OL,8,     Gband to superstardom. The story
OL,9,     Gof how Queen created their
OL,10,     Gseminal fourth album.
OL,11,G1900FQueen: Live At The Rainbow
OL,12,     GA treat for all Queen fans as
OL,13,     GFreddie, Brian, John and Roger
OL,14,     Gperform early hits such as Killer
OL,15,     GQueen and Seven Seas of Rhye at
OL,16,     Gthe Rainbow Theatre in London in
OL,17,     G1974.
